      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Russell Reagan</b>\n</p><p><b>Russell Reagan</b>,<br />\nan American software developer, chess programmer and author of apparently private chess engines \n<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>, \nearly <a href=\"/Bitboards\" title=\"Bitboards\">Bitboard</a> promoter <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, \nand until 2015 active poster in <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Computer Chess Forums</a>. In 2004, Russell served as moderator in <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Russell_Reagan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Russell_Reagan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/rec.games.chess.computer/r5-Kdb4p4bE/tKCt-SwZKlgJ\">Winboard for Dummies</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Russell Reagan</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, June 30, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=198907\">High NPS vs. Low NPS</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Russell Reagan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 25, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/Nodes_per_Second\" title=\"Nodes per Second\">Nodes per Second</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=242025\">Promotion frequency</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Russell Reagan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 23, 2002</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/rec.games.chess.computer/C8B8rM8DeYM/fQ_3AD6DcDYJ\">Re: Object-Oriented Chess Program</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Russell Reagan</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, August 31, 2002</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=261036\">Re: attacks_from[] and attacks_to[] info</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Russell Reagan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 22, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/Kogge-Stone_Algorithm\" title=\"Kogge-Stone Algorithm\">Kogge-Stone Algorithm</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=266044\">Re: Differences between 0x88, 10x12 and Bitboards!?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Russell Reagan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 19, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/0x88\" title=\"0x88\">0x88</a>, <a href=\"/10x12_Board\" title=\"10x12 Board\">10x12 Board</a>, <a href=\"/Bitboards\" title=\"Bitboards\">Bitboards</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=273558\">Aspiration search, PVS</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Russell Reagan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 28, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/Aspiration_Windows\" title=\"Aspiration Windows\">Aspiration Windows</a>, <a href=\"/Principal_Variation_Search\" title=\"Principal Variation Search\">PVS</a>, <a href=\"/PVS_and_Aspiration\" title=\"PVS and Aspiration\">PVS and Aspiration</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=274926\">kiwipete perft position</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Russell Reagan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 04, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Perft_Results#kiwipete\" title=\"Perft Results\">Perft Results - kiwipete</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=296689\">Testing the reliability of forward pruning</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Russell Reagan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 15, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Pruning\" title=\"Pruning\">Pruning</a>, <a href=\"/Engine_Testing\" title=\"Engine Testing\">Engine Testing</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=298973\">TSCP with bitboards</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Russell Reagan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 01, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/TSCP\" title=\"TSCP\">TSCP</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=301402\">PVS and MTD(f) branching factor</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Russell Reagan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 17, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Principal_Variation_Search\" title=\"Principal Variation Search\">PVS</a>, <a href=\"/MTD(f)\" title=\"MTD(f)\">MTD(f)</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=304136\">Fail high reductions</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Russell Reagan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 01, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Fail-High_Reductions\" title=\"Fail-High Reductions\">Fail-High Reductions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=314585\">Fail soft alpha-beta</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Russell Reagan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 08, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Fail-Soft\" title=\"Fail-Soft\">Fail-Soft</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Russell_Reagan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=18608&amp;start=3\">Re: need suggestion for callable Chess engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Russell Reagan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 28, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=19837&amp;start=6\">Re: compact bitboard move generator</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Russell Reagan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 26, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/Bitboard_Serialization\" title=\"Bitboard Serialization\">Bitboard Serialization</a>, <a href=\"/Move_Generation\" title=\"Move Generation\">Move Generation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=26817\">Speed/ELO relationship, and question to engine programmers</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Russell Reagan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 02, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Playing_Strength\" title=\"Playing Strength\">Playing Strength</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Russell_Reagan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=34762\">Simple open source program wanted</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Russell Reagan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 06, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=44064\">Go language</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Russell Reagan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 15, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Go_(Programming_Language)\" title=\"Go (Programming Language)\">Go (Programming Language)</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=44813\">Virtualization and multi-processor engines</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Russell Reagan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 16, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=49562\">Simplest bitboard attack generation</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Russell Reagan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 03, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Sliding_Piece_Attacks\" title=\"Sliding Piece Attacks\">Sliding Piece Attacks</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=49675\">Are there any chess engines written in D?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Russell Reagan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 12, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/D_(Programming_Language)\" title=\"D (Programming Language)\">D (Programming Language)</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=51883\">Reducing tablebase size with search</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Russell Reagan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 07, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Endgame_Tablebases\" title=\"Endgame Tablebases\">Endgame Tablebases</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=52083\">Move encoding</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Russell Reagan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 21, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Encoding_Moves\" title=\"Encoding Moves\">Encoding Moves</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=52214\">Position validity</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Russell Reagan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 04, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Chess_Position\" title=\"Chess Position\">Chess Position</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Russell_Reagan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=55934\">Methods for playing human-like chess</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Russell Reagan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 07, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=56255\">Automated comparison of human chess players</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Russell Reagan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 06, 2015</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Russell_Reagan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/review/R3Q8OCBBE3J98S\">Review</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Russell Reagan</a> on <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://store.doverpublications.com/0486264866.html\">Pawn Power in Chess (Dover Chess)</a> by <a href=\"/Hans_Kmoch\" title=\"Hans Kmoch\">Hans Kmoch</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amazon.com\">Amazons.com</a>, August 18, 2001</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Russell_Reagan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></spa